1. Figured out what items were bought, for how much, and by whom
   1. Calculate the shared buying cost (function)
2. For each item, figured out what items were shared by whom (LLM)
   1. Calculate the shared cost (function)
3. For each person
   1. Summed up the amount they spent (function)
   2. Summed up the amount they used/shared (function)
   3. Calculate net value
4. Sort debtors and creditors from largest --> smallest